title: Is a Hotdog a Sandwhich?
description: Is a Hot Dog a Sandwich is a longstanding argument regarding whether hot dogs served in a sliced bun can be considered a type of sandwich.

title: Cats vs Dogs
description: Cats and dogs are the most popular pets in the world. Cats are more independent and are generally cheaper and less demanding pets. Dogs are loyal and obedient but require more attention and exercise, including regular walks.

title: Is A Pop Tart A Calzone?
description: Is a pop tart a calzone? This is one question that has troubled many people for years. The answer is not so simple, but some say yes because of its shape while others say no because of its taste."
